2005-07-11  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* Ig3DViewpointsCategory.h, Ig3DViewpointsCategory.cc: New static
	methods are adde to set a view point from camera and a camera from view
	point. Make use of new SoSFEnum cameraType to set the camera type
	correctly before applying the view point. Code cleanup. Fixed the view
	point category bug #9397 by properly calling the focusOut.

